content.rendered:
After a nervous breakdown, Walter swaps the city for the countryside. However, his hopes for a peaceful life are dashed when he meets his new neighbors.

Director: Roberto Santucci

Writer: Paulo Cursino

Stars: Maurício Manfrini. Leandro Hassum. Júlia Rabello
